product_description.downstream_description: Combining elegance and superior function in one piece, the Alena finish wood free standing cheval mirror jewelry armoire provides you with a better way to store your jewelry. Modern and contemporary, this length cheval mirror slides open to reveal a deep, line jewelry storage compartments. Engineered wood construction comes in your choice of finish, the ideal addition to any bedroom. This stylish piece of furniture is great for ladies that love their jeweler displayed in a classy way. It makes it easy to choose your jeweler in the morning without the frustration of loofor loose, missing pieces. It stores all of your jeweler safely and in an organized manner. Made in china, the Alena jewelry armoire requires assembly.
